Description:
    Generates a Rails migration for income records with specified period types.
    This generator supports two period types: 'year_quarter' and 'date_range'.

Usage:
    bin/rails generate flex:income_records_migration NAME period_type

Examples:
    bin/rails generate flex:income_records_migration CreateIncomeRecords year_quarter
    bin/rails generate flex:income_records_migration CreateIncomeRecords date_range

Supported Period Types:
    year_quarter - Creates columns: period_year (:integer), period_quarter (:integer)
    date_range   - Creates columns: period_start (:date), period_end (:date)

This will create:
    A Rails migration file with the appropriate column definitions for the specified period type, as well as any additional columns defined in the generator.
